Nodes / XTEC Blocs: Localization tools and messages
===============================================================================

Update the translations:

    $ bash update.sh <project> <git-branch>

Create a translation memory:

    $ bash digest.sh <project>

Requeriments:

    gettext                 Localization tools
    wp-cli                  WordPress command line interface

Generated folders:
    
    output/<project>        Project folders
    
    ./tools                 WordPress localization tools
    ./branch                Branch to translate
    ./master                Stable branch from which to pull translation
    ./pot                   Generated translation templates
    ./po/master             Stable branch translation
    ./po/upstream           Oficial WordPress translations
    ./po/branch             Updated translations

References:
    
    GNU gettext utilities
    https://www.gnu.org/software/gettext/manual/html_node/index.html
    
    I18n for WordPress Developers
    https://codex.wordpress.org/I18n_for_WordPress_Developers
    
    The command line interface for WordPress
    http://wp-cli.org/
